OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FThames Water will pay an extra #18.2
OL,8,Fmillion for breaking rules related to
OL,9,Fdividend payments, the first ever
OL,10,Fdividend-related fine, Ofwat said.
OL,12,FThe watchdog pointed to dividends of
OL,13,F#37.5 million in October 2023 and
OL,14,F#131.3 million in March 2024.
OL,16,FThe firm is currently in a "cash lock-
OL,17,Fup" period and no more dividends can
OL,18,Fbe paid without approval from the
OL,19,Fregulator.
