OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FMr Black added: "We will not stand by
OL,8,Fwhen companies pay undeserved
OL,9,Fdividends to their shareholders."
OL,11,FOfwat said the money will be paid by
OL,12,Fthe utility giant and its investors,
OL,13,Fnot by customers.
OL,15,FEnvironment Secretary Steve Reed said:
OL,16,F"The era of profiting from failure is
OL,17,Fover. The Government is cleaning up
OL,18,Four rivers, lakes and seas for good."
OL,20,FThe wastewater fine was first proposed
OL,21,Flast year and confirmed on Wednesday.
