OL,3,CThames Water hit with biggest ever
OL,4,Cfine of #122.7m over pollution and
OL,5,Cdividends
OL,7,FA Thames Water spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Ftake our responsibility towards the
OL,9,Fenvironment very seriously and note
OL,10,Fthat Ofwat acknowledges we have
OL,11,Falready made progress to address
OL,12,Fissues raised in the investigation
OL,13,Frelating to storm overflows.
OL,15,F"The dividends were declared following
OL,16,Fa consideration of the company's legal
OL,17,Fand regulatory obligations.
OL,19,F"Our lenders continue to support our
OL,20,Fliquidity position and our equity
OL,21,Fraise process continues."
